author: Dr. Delaram J. Taghipour
title: Questions remain over whether COVID-19 recovery will guarantee immunity
description: Understanding whether people build immunity could help reopen economies around the world.
content: It has been only 101 days since a cluster of cases of pneumonia in Wuhan, China, were reported to the World Health Organization, and already our understanding of the deadly COVID-19 pandemic seems extraordinary. But even with over 1.6 million people infected … [+5947 chars]
